# 🎙️ नेपाली SEO उपकरण | Nepali Voice-Based Keyword Generator

A simple, open-source SEO keyword generator built for Nepali content creators. Speak or type your ideas in Nepali and instantly get 100 keyword suggestions with search volume, difficulty, and CPC estimates.

👉 **Live Demo**: [Click here to use the tool](https://99blogger.github.io/Nepali-s-SEO-Tool/)

---

## 📌 Features

- 🎤 Voice-to-text input in Nepali
- 🔑 Generates 100 unique keyword combinations
- 📊 Shows random SEO metrics (to be replaced with real data soon)
- 📥 Export keywords to CSV or copy with 1 click
- 🌓 Dark mode support
- 💻 100% static site — no backend, runs in your browser

